name: Freeport Republic Ship Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the more common ship hulls and fighter LPCs from the "Killia Drive Yards" school of design.

name: Freeport Republic Weapon Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the weapons from the "Killia Drive Yards" school of design.

name: Freeport Republic Mobile Suit Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct "Killia Drive Yard's KMS-119" Line of Mobile Suit LCPs.

name: Freeport Republic Advanced Mobile Suit Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct "Killia Drive Yard's KMS-129" Line of Advanced Mobile Suit LCPs.

name: Farstar Mechatronics Mobile Suit Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct "Farstar Mechatronic's FM-06MS Leo" Line of Mobile Suit LCPs.
